cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a decision tree ensemble approach that is highly competitive to deep neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) since the proposed approach can be applied to image classification tasks. The paper also mentions the efficiency and scalability of the proposed approach, which suggests that it could be relevant to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
